				"string" : "The defaults are useful, but you might still want to specialize them. For example, in the chat below, we start from a default GT chat, but we extend it with explanations and a response for parsing a given string. In this specific case, we ask it to execute the code before proposing, a request which should get the LLM to use the code evaluation tool:"
